Any Halfling, dwarf or gnome ( They make great doorstops.)
Oh yeah Inkeep Juna (My first encounter with a non Darkelf NPC didnt go so
well )

Lothaniel T'Kazz
Mighty Tier'Dal Warrior of the 36th Rank.
